{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"7608ace0-a539-454e-88d5-91e7efac1c76","content":"This is a well-known MTP behavioral difference. **Exit code 8 = \"no tests discovered\"**. VSTest returned 0 in that case; MTP treats it as a failure.\n\nYou have three ways to fix it:\n\n### Option 1 — CI command line (recommended)\n```bash\ndotnet test --ignore-exit-code 8\n```\n\n### Option 2 — Environment variable (good for CI matrix)\n```bash\nexport TESTINGPLATFORM_EXITCODE_IGNORE=8\ndotnet test\n```\n\n### Option 3 — Project file (applies everywhere)\nAdd this property to your `.csproj`:\n\n```xml\n<TestingPlatformExitCodeIgnore>8</TestingPlatformExitCodeIgnore>\n```\n\nSince your `ConditionalTests.cs` is entirely behind `#if INCLUDE_SLOW_TESTS`, builds without that symbol produce an empty test assembly — triggering exit code 8.\n\nI'd recommend **Option 1** so the fix is explicit in your CI pipeline. Want me to apply Option 3 to your project file instead?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"0bd1968b-1fd6-4785-bf6e-d684cf332c30","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"Now I understand the issue clearly. With MTP, when no tests are discovered (because the `INCLUDE_SLOW_TESTS` symbol isn't defined), the runner returns exit code 8 (which means \"no tests found\"). VSTest returned 0 in this case.\n\nThe fix is to use the `--ignore-exit-code` option or the `TESTINGPLATFORM_EXITCODE_IGNORE` environment variable to tell MTP to treat \"no tests discovered\" as success.\n\nSpecifically, there are a few approaches:\n\n1. **`--ignore-exit-code 8`** on the `dotnet test` command line\n\n\n2. **`TESTINGPLATFORM_EXITCODE_IGNORE=8`** environment variable\n3. **MSBuild property `TestingPlatformExitCodeIgnore`** in the project file\n\nAny of these will resolve the issue by instructing MTP to ignore the exit code 8 and treat it as a successful run.","outputTokens":468,"requestId":"9C4F:1554C1:160D853:18A9538:69F861A0"},"id":"591190a5-35e0-4be4-b30b-2ff1c4df76bd","timestamp":"2026-05-04T09:06:52.861Z","parentId":"c9c45f7e-4761-4f21-9244-6454aca22711"}
